name: The Garden Massacre
description: Blood-stained screens. The smell in the air brought a feeling of sadness and bitterness. Fights, joys, futures, all of this, all of this, in order to reach nothing at the end. At the end of the journey. Among the young sighs of the young Kenmaru, a goddess of the four swords spoke to him in a peaceful and lively place. "I lend you my power in exchange for your services." With a grudge and anger in his heart, the young man did not think twice, and accepted. He became the avatar of the goddess.
